Favored Follower
/Ancient-Aetherium/placeholder.png
Cost: 1000(750)[500]
Backgrounds: Arcane, Follower, Tailor
Known by their Founder as a dependable follower, your character is able to preserve their boons should their Founder allow it. When any amount of Boons are spent, make a Persuasion Skill Check with a Difficulty of 3. Should the success pass, no Boons are consumed.
